00:05:57,881 --> 00:05:59,256
[loud buzzer]

67
00:06:08,367 --> 00:06:09,660
[changing assembly line noises]

68
00:06:49,171 --> 00:06:50,571
[choral music begins]

69
00:07:26,638 --> 00:07:27,786
-Senn, get over here!

70
00:07:28,185 --> 00:07:29,985
