until the next prod cycle.

83
00:08:41,483 --> 00:08:42,520
Bastards.

84
00:08:42,545 --> 00:08:44,364
I knew I'd find you two
love units up here.

85
00:08:44,388 --> 00:08:45,475
Hi, Resh.

86
00:08:45,499 --> 00:08:47,499
Kana, darling, mind if I join?

87
