that a few days ago.

173
00:18:05,347 --> 00:18:08,565
So ridiculous. Huge spaceships
don't land on planets.

174
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:10,129
Everybody knows that.

175
00:18:12,276 --> 00:18:14,292
So, what about
Lann... don't tell me...

176
00:18:14,332 --> 00:18:15,761
