177
00:18:15,785 --> 00:18:18,245
Aw, that's awful. You must be crushed.

178
00:18:18,269 --> 00:18:20,269
Look, you know the crew
chief in Bio, right?

179
00:18:20,293 --> 00:18:21,806
Do you think you could
talk to her for me?

180
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,191
